      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要给Education_ContentCDN项目画一个Git流程图，展示从main分支合并到未开发分支的过程。标题就叫\"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch (Education_ContentCDN)\"吧。",
