      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下。先放title，然后TB方向布局，从第一个commit开始，branch develop，develop上再commit，checkout回main做commit，再checkout develop，最后merge main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
